> Hi Gary,
>
> very good chance its the nut that hold the wiper arm onto the rotating 
> spindle has worked loose. Just pop the plastic dome cover off and 
> tighten with a 10mm spanner.
>
> If it's not that then possibly the splines are striped from the end of 
> the spindle or in the arm in which case the 'offending' part needs to 
> be replaced.
>
> Good luck
